    "However, when looking carefully into the feedback, we find that many feedback describe the quality of the response but do not provide constructive criticism (i.e.",
    "areas that can be improved to make the response better).",
    "This means that there are often fewer than three actionable suggestions for the Edit model to act upon.",
    "Concretely, we estimate there to be around two effective feedback.",
    "To solve this issue, we increase the number of feedback generated and re-rank feedback based on a heuristic: the number of constructive criticism keywords foot_1 they contain."
